# Goi thu API server (Phase 1). Can extension "REST Client" (humao.rest-client):
# mo file nay, bam "Send Request" phia tren moi muc.
# Truoc do chay server: uvicorn server.main:app --reload

@base = http://localhost:8000

### Suc khoe + backend dang dung
GET {{base}}/health

### Liet ke thiet bi
GET {{base}}/devices

### Tier 1 — bat den phong khach (tat dinh, ~ms)
POST {{base}}/command/text
Content-Type: application/json

{ "text": "bật đèn phòng khách" }

### Tier 1 — ngu canh bot phong ngu: "bat den" -> den phong ngu
POST {{base}}/command/text
Content-Type: application/json

{ "text": "bật đèn", "bot_id": "bot_bed1_01" }

### Tier 1 — dat nhiet do (gioi han 16-30)
POST {{base}}/command/text
Content-Type: application/json

{ "text": "chỉnh điều hòa phòng ngủ 25 độ" }

### Tier 1 — lenh nhom
POST {{base}}/command/text
Content-Type: application/json

{ "text": "tắt hết đèn" }

### Tier 1 — scene
POST {{base}}/command/text
Content-Type: application/json

{ "text": "tôi đi ngủ đây" }

### Tier 3 — cau mo ho, can LLM (Ollama phai chay)
POST {{base}}/command/text
Content-Type: application/json

{ "text": "nóng quá" }

### Do tre theo tang + ti le trung cache
GET {{base}}/metrics

### Xoa cache intent
DELETE {{base}}/cache
